<plot>Dan Donahue has finally met the woman of his dreams. But on the night he is going to propose, he is overcome by deep-rooted anger caused by the father who abandoned him as a boy. Dan confronts his feelings of bitterness head on as he pours his heart out in a letter to his father. Based on a true story, A Letter to Dad is a touching story of how faith, love, and spirituality can overcome a lifetime of pain and anger.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?012257</url></doc>
